      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, confirming the mechanical health of the internal rotating assembly. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with a well-maintained driver, the suspension geometry remains true, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the precise feedback these coupes are known for. A mechanically sound enthusiast's car ready for the apex.",
